How to play "Super Survivors":
At first you have to start the game and click the "START GAME" - Button.
Now you have to choose between the left and right character, to choose you have to click on one of their Pictures.
After clicking on one of said pictures you see their Stat-Screen next to them.
Now the "Choose"-button is enabled and you can click him.
Based on the chosen character a different Player figure will appear.
An enemy that spawns at a random x-coordinate will try to follow and kill you.

What you should be able to do at this screen:
Moving the character by tilting your screen in the direction you want to move.